attributes.mlflow.spanInputs: {"prompt": "Configure model-driven telemetry for ISIS on IOS XR with server 10.10.10.10:5432, tcp, sample interval 60000ms."}
attributes.mlflow.spanOutputs:
"telemetry model-driven
 sensor-group ISIS-STATE
  sensor-path Cisco-IOS-XR-infra-xtc-agent-oper:xtc/topology-nodes/topology-node/ipv4-link/remote-node-protocol-identifier/igp-information/igp/isis
  sensor-path Cisco-IOS-XR-clns-isis-oper:isis/instances/instance/nsr-status/isis-nsr-infra/te
 !
 destination-group DG-GRPC
  address-family ipv4
   destination 10.10.10.10
    port 5432
    encoding self-describing-gpb
    protocol grpc no-tls
 !
 subscription SUB-ISIS
  sensor-group-id ISIS-STATE sample-interval 60000
  destination-group-id DG-GRPC
 !"
